INSERT INTO mstr.advisor_memo_report VALUES (1127, 22911, 1687, '1599218', '2024-05-31 16:39:31', 'Pal, Aditya', 'Roy, Devika Rose', 'Accuracy of CRQ - see page 28 of Sustainability report "Reduce GHG emissions to464,472 tCO2eq by 2025" - these are Scope 1 and 2.For the base year, please check if this target is available in previous years reports (2021, 2020, 2019, etc) and apply that base year. If this is the first year they report the target then use 2022. Current level you have, and you can also compute reduction etc', 'First year of reporting this target, 2022 has been used as base year', '2001769', '2024-06-03 11:23:48', '1900-01-01 00:00:00', '1900-01-01 00:00:00', '1900-01-01 00:00:00', '2025-05-25 00:00:00', 3509, 'CTP3', 'esg_navigiator', '01');
INSERT INTO mstr.advisor_memo_report VALUES (1128, 22659, 1664, '1493184', '2024-05-29 17:36:55', 'Gurunathan, Akshay Ram', 'Leva, Aljaz', 'Analytical:  Can you confirm if 99% crude oil here refers to oil only, its hrd to believe that only 1% is from gas', 'This is the only information I was able to obtain from BCA pt. 2: "EMSS plays a key role within the Group, as its primary function is the purchase and sale of crude oil on behalf of Exxon internationally. EMSS revenues increased to $84.9bn. EMSS’ cost structure is almost entirely made up of crude oil and product purchases ($84.2bn).". If that might be misleading, we can drop this information and rather use Group''s data: Oil- 2,397 vs. gas (in BOE)- 3,688= split of 39% vs. 61%.  Please let us know. ', '1664889', '2024-06-03 12:21:55', '1900-01-01 00:00:00', '1900-01-01 00:00:00', '1900-01-01 00:00:00', '2025-05-25 00:00:00', 3414, 'GTR3', 'esg_navigiator', '01');
INSERT INTO mstr.advisor_memo_report VALUES (1129, 22659, 1665, '1493184', '2024-05-29 17:38:29', 'Gurunathan, Akshay Ram', 'Leva, Aljaz', 'Analytical:  What is the diffference between flaring intensity and methane intensity. What is upstream intensity ? (do you mean the upstream part of the business?)', 'Group''s targets are slightly  hard to understand since not clearly disclosed. However, these targets were taken from the website and were previously confirmed with Elliott. Could you please guide us on how else should we record them to reflect appropriate picture? "Our 2030 plans are expected to result in a 20%-30% reduction in corporate-wide greenhouse gas intensity, including reductions of 40%-50% in upstream intensity, 70%-80% in corporate-wide methane intensity and 60%-70% in corporate-wide flaring intensity. These plans apply to Scope 1 and 2 greenhouse gas emissions from our operated assets versus 2016 levels. " ', '1664889', '2024-06-03 12:35:25', '1900-01-01 00:00:00', '1900-01-01 00:00:00', '1900-01-01 00:00:00', '2025-05-25 00:00:00', 3509, 'CTP3', 'esg_navigiator', '01');
INSERT INTO mstr.advisor_memo_report VALUES (1130, 24650, 1695, '1489063', '2024-06-03 15:02:26', 'Masarin, Lisa', 'Scariah, Renjith ', 'I don''t see any evidence of switching the production mix of products / low carbon alternatives. Given this is a project as well, it is unlikely that this will focus on that change in business model, and more focused on financing acquisition.I also don''t see any CCUS evidence here. There is primarily a lot of commitment towards improving energy efficiecny with new systems and processes. There is a very small piece on moving from Gas to electric power consumption, but the levels of this are not available, and so I would ad this in the commentary that this is a risk (maybe even remove that selection as well) because no quantification available.Can add "Other non-core" updates for the LED lightbulbs :)', 'Climate Analyst comment: The options removed. Space constraint in the free text field hence comment added in transition risk section of outcome.', '1540001', '2024-06-03 16:39:24', '1900-01-01 00:00:00', '1900-01-01 00:00:00', '1900-01-01 00:00:00', '2025-05-25 00:00:00', 3511, 'CTP3', 'esg_navigiator', '01');
INSERT INTO mstr.advisor_memo_report VALUES (1131, 24629, 1699, '1489063', '2024-06-05 15:24:44', 'Gurunathan, Akshay Ram', 'Kumar, Ajith', 'They are a dedicated mining company , so would change this from "Others" to "Mining". They mine iron ore, lithium as well as having energy generation assets across Western Australia.', 'Agreed - amended', '1286637', '2024-06-06 07:02:23', '1900-01-01 00:00:00', '1900-01-01 00:00:00', '1900-01-01 00:00:00', '2025-05-25 00:00:00', 3412, 'GTR3', 'esg_navigiator', '01');
