INSERT INTO mstr.advisor_memo_report VALUES (1462, 24711, 2120, '1575987', '2024-09-24 05:28:29', 'Leva, Aljaz', 'Brodzicka, Elzbieta', 'Do we have percentage of sales to Europe ?', 'ADDITIONAL INFORMATION. The is no % of sales published. However, BCA include information that: "EZDK is by far the Group’s largest subsidiary and contributor to the consolidated revenue" & "A significant proportion of Ezz Steel Group exports are destined for Europe, Asia, and the USA. "', '2007983', '2024-10-04 08:01:04', '1900-01-01 00:00:00', '1900-01-01 00:00:00', '1900-01-01 00:00:00', '2025-05-25 00:00:00', 3425, 'GTR3', 'esg_navigiator', '01');
INSERT INTO mstr.advisor_memo_report VALUES (1463, 24711, 2121, '1575987', '2024-09-24 05:38:44', 'Leva, Aljaz', 'Brodzicka, Elzbieta', 'p. 8Ezz Steel follows strict control strategies emphasizing our environmental protection management process via various engineering, management, and technical means to ensure the compliance of the discharged pollutants and the continuous improvement of all the primary environmental protection indicators. We continually invest in technologies to achieve the highest environmental performance standards and have made significant strides in recent years to reduce our environmental impact." - Does not include any details on the measures undertaken the comments are therefore not relevant. "Waste Management: Ezz Steel contributes to a resource recycling society by recycling by-products generated by steelworks as much as possible. We manage our “by-product recycling rate” or “material efficiency rate” as KPIs material efficiency rate indicates the percentage of utilized product, by-products, and waste to total output material.The following figur', 'Noted. Additionally information obtained from the CA and from new BCA Part 2 have been added to the comment.', '2007983', '2024-10-04 08:11:01', '1900-01-01 00:00:00', '1900-01-01 00:00:00', '1900-01-01 00:00:00', '2025-05-25 00:00:00', 3511, 'CTP3', 'esg_navigiator', '01');
INSERT INTO mstr.advisor_memo_report VALUES (1464, 25590, 2153, '1489063', '2024-10-04 14:25:22', 'Gurunathan, Akshay Ram', 'Kumar, Ajith', 'The types of emissions you are talking about are not CO2 emissions and pollutants are not nearly as detrimental from a climate risk perspective. Given they are a pharma company, the level of direct emissions will be very small in comparison to high emitting industries. They report under 1m tonnes of emission across all 3 scopes in their latest report. An O&G producer (Exxon) for example reported 100m tonnes just Scope 1 and 2 emissions, where Scope 3 make up 80%.Therefore in the global emissions levels reliance, this is very small. Please change to Low.', 'agreed - Amended thanks', '1286637', '2024-10-04 16:16:57', '1900-01-01 00:00:00', '1900-01-01 00:00:00', '1900-01-01 00:00:00', '2025-05-25 00:00:00', 3402, 'GTR3', 'esg_navigiator', '01');
INSERT INTO mstr.advisor_memo_report VALUES (1465, 25524, 2155, '1551380', '2024-10-06 14:47:21', 'Radhakrishnan, Gowtham ', 'Jen, Yvonne ', 'Answer selection here is "Additional policy measures expected in next 2 years" but analysis in outcome tab says "driven by policy measures that is not expected in next 10 years"', 'Agreed. Changed in the outcome tab to" additional policy measures expected in next 2 years".', '1600990', '2024-10-07 06:51:56', '1900-01-01 00:00:00', '1900-01-01 00:00:00', '1900-01-01 00:00:00', '2025-05-25 00:00:00', 3425, 'GTR3', 'esg_navigiator', '01');
INSERT INTO mstr.advisor_memo_report VALUES (1466, 25652, 2156, '1575987', '2024-10-07 05:10:38', 'Joardar, Abhisek ', 'Pai, Vallabhi Vishwas', 'Please explain how Vessel Collision avoidance measures is a Physical risk adaptation plan. ', 'HHI specialising in shipbuilding is using ''maritime control centre'' to montor its vessels in real time. Therefore in the events of extreme weather events, that can lead to vessel-damage and/or vessel collision, the martime control centre hence plays a role in such risk aversion. Therefore, it can be considered as a physical risk adaptation plan. ', '2019328', '2024-10-07 13:55:07', '1900-01-01 00:00:00', '1900-01-01 00:00:00', '1900-01-01 00:00:00', '2025-05-25 00:00:00', 3304, 'PRA3', 'esg_navigiator', '01');
INSERT INTO mstr.advisor_memo_report VALUES (1467, 25652, 2157, '1575987', '2024-10-07 05:22:02', 'Joardar, Abhisek ', 'Pai, Vallabhi Vishwas', 'The split should not be used here . It will lead to data discrepancy at portfolio level', 'Agreed with the feedback. Changes made accordingly ', '2019328', '2024-10-07 13:57:05', '1900-01-01 00:00:00', '1900-01-01 00:00:00', '1900-01-01 00:00:00', '2025-05-25 00:00:00', 3417, 'GTR3', 'esg_navigiator', '01');
INSERT INTO mstr.advisor_memo_report VALUES (1468, 25652, 2158, '1575987', '2024-10-07 05:23:05', 'Joardar, Abhisek ', 'Pai, Vallabhi Vishwas', 'Price of Carbon under K ETS seems to be incorrect. The current prices are roughly USD 6 per tonne of Co2 . Coverage of sector covered and emission covered has also undergone a change. Please check if EEXI and CII regulations are applicable on Rigs. ', 'The price of KETS is amended, along with the sector coverage. The EEXI and CII regulations are applicable to Rigs, which has already been captured in the comment. ', '2019328', '2024-10-07 14:55:47', '1900-01-01 00:00:00', '1900-01-01 00:00:00', '1900-01-01 00:00:00', '2025-05-25 00:00:00', 3425, 'GTR3', 'esg_navigiator', '01');
INSERT INTO mstr.advisor_memo_report VALUES (1469, 25652, 2159, '1575987', '2024-10-07 06:02:46', 'Joardar, Abhisek ', 'Pai, Vallabhi Vishwas', 'Is 2018 Scope 1 intensity correct ? - Why it has jumped sharply in 2019 despite not such significant jump in scope 1 emission from 2018 to 2019 ?', 'Please note that the scope 1 & scope 3 emissions are auto-populated from S&P from 2018 to 2021. Hence, we are unable to justify the emissions progress from 2018-19.Additional comment referring to reduction in emission intensity from 2021 to 2022 (as per CDP) is captured in comment Q5.5.1', '2019328', '2024-10-07 15:00:27', '1900-01-01 00:00:00', '1900-01-01 00:00:00', '1900-01-01 00:00:00', '2025-05-25 00:00:00', 3507, 'CTP3', 'esg_navigiator', '01');
INSERT INTO mstr.advisor_memo_report VALUES (1470, 24534, 2162, '1575987', '2024-10-07 07:10:26', 'Komjati, Dalma Beatrix ', 'Pai, Vallabhi Vishwas', 'Korean ETS price currently USD 6 , In korea Shipping is also covered in ETS', 'updated as per the feedback', '2019328', '2024-10-07 15:28:37', '1900-01-01 00:00:00', '1900-01-01 00:00:00', '1900-01-01 00:00:00', '2025-05-25 00:00:00', 3425, 'GTR3', 'esg_navigiator', '01');
INSERT INTO mstr.advisor_memo_report VALUES (1472, 25982, 2149, '1575987', '2024-10-04 13:41:54', 'Ptasinska, Dorota', 'Jen, Yvonne ', '"Also, they are strengthening employee training and designing green buildings according to local conditions." - Not a Physical risk adaptation ', 'Agreed. Removed the sentence.', '1600990', '2024-10-08 06:46:09', '1900-01-01 00:00:00', '1900-01-01 00:00:00', '1900-01-01 00:00:00', '2025-05-25 00:00:00', 3304, 'PRA3', 'esg_navigiator', '01');
